Comment: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Comment: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes.
Comment: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same color as your eyes.
Comment: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I felt when I saw this...
Comment: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Comment: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it called?
Comment: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Major Gilbert.
Comment: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in the hospital\Nfor 120 days now.
Comment: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My strength has almost recovered.
Comment: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Movement is still a little difficult,
Comment: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can perform my duties.
Comment: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me return to my post soon."
Comment: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,KINGDOM OF ENCIEL\NSOMEWHERE IN THE CAPITAL OF ENCHAINE
Comment: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Her existence\Nwas hidden from everyone.
Comment: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,However, people who knew about her\Nsaid that she was a weapon.
Comment: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She would fight if you ordered her to.
Comment: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She just looked like a human.
Comment: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just a tool...
Comment: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,without a heart.
Comment: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Colonel Hodgins.
Comment: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come this way.
Comment: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh.
Comment: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Comment: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Comment: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Comment: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Comment: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Comment: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the major?
Comment: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Major Gilbert?
Comment: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Comment: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Comment: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he return home?
Comment: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How are his injuries?
Comment: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,His injuries were severe.
Comment: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the major...
Comment: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,alive?
Comment: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Comment: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They've given us permission to\Ndischarge you from the hospital.
Comment: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Colonel Hodgins came all this way\Nto pick you up.
Comment: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's right.
Comment: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Lt. Colonel Hodgins.
Comment: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. Relax.
Comment: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten you were a Lt. Colonel.
Comment: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Comment: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Comment: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Comment: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways. So, you do remember me?
Comment: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We've met twice. Once during training\Nand the night before the battle.
Comment: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're right.
Comment: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing?
Comment: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I was writing a report to Major Gilbert.
Comment: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that writing words\Nwould be good for my recovery.
Comment: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the major well?
Comment: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Violet.
Comment: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me to come here.
Comment: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that means he's fine.
Comment: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor told me that we won the war.
Comment: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What post is he assigned to now?
Comment: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When shall I join him?
Comment: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get changed first. I'll have them\Nsend the car in the meantime.
Comment: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,These finally arrived.\NThey're your belongings.
Comment: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they mistakenly delivered it\Nto an army base far away.
Comment: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The brooch.
Comment: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The emerald brooch.
Comment: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is everything from the garrison\Nand the place where they found you.
Comment: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go look for it if it's not here.
Comment: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Comment: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a gift.
Comment: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The major gave it to me!
Comment: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Comment: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look for it.
Comment: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Comment: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-You must...
Comment: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,come with me.
Comment: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,These are his orders.
Comment: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders?
Comment: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Comment: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When will I receive the next order\Nfrom the major?
Comment: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm limited to only performing certain\Nduties because of my current condition.
Comment: 0,0:06:26.85,0:06:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. Congratulations\Non getting discharged.
Comment: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what you'd like, so,\NI bought three. What do you think?
Comment: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need them.
Comment: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You have to choose one.
Comment: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretend that the world is about to end.\NOkay. Three, two...
Comment: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... the puppy.
Comment: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Comment: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you choose the puppy?
Comment: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The major's brother once told me,
Comment: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're Gilbert's dog."
Comment: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a long journey.
Comment: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The train tracks around here\Nwere damaged during the bombing
Comment: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and aren't usable anymore.
Comment: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been to Leiden before?
Comment: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Comment: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Comment: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Live...
Comment: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and be free.
Comment: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,From the bottom of my heart.
Comment: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Comment: 0,0:07:58.86,0:07:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Colonel.
Comment: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is. The port of Leiden.
Comment: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,LEIDEN, THE CAPITAL OF\NLEIDENSCHAFTLICH
Comment: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert was thinking about\Nyour future after the war.
Comment: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted to leave you\Nwith the Evergarden household,
Comment: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,his most trusted relatives.
Comment: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I contacted them,
Comment: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and the couple said they'd be happy\Nto take you in.
Comment: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Comment: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Violet.
Comment: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the lady of the\NEvergarden household.
Comment: 0,0:08:58.42,0:08:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Say your greetings.
Comment: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A bow would suffice.
Comment: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it take around three days\Nfrom Enchaine now?
Comment: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Normally, I'd be able\Nto return in one day.
Comment: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But the war has been going on\Nfor four years.
Comment: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to take some more time\Nto restore everything.
Comment: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Comment: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some tea.
Comment: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry. Don't force yourself.
Comment: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! You'll get burned.
Comment: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem. I can't feel heat.
Comment: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But your bandages...\NQuick, we have to cool them down.
Comment: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oliver, bring some ice!\N-Yes, madam.
Comment: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These arms are made of adamant silver.
Comment: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a bit bulky, but they're sturdy.
Comment: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not accustomed to them yet.\NI should be able to adjust soon.
Comment: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come this way for a minute?
Comment: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I used these when I was young.
Comment: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice. Try them on.
Comment: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They look good on you.
Comment: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Comment: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to get going now.
Comment: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get back to the office.
Comment: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Comment: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to Tiffany, okay?
Comment: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Comment: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Comment: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of me as your real mother.
Comment: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me anything. Okay?
Comment: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have parents, so,\NI don't need any replacements.
Comment: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Comment: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a son,
Comment: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but he was killed in the war.
Comment: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't become a replacement\Nfor your lost child.
Comment: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. Gilbert's wish\Nis for you to happily live here.
Comment: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you understand?
Comment: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The major.
Comment: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The major. Why is he leaving me here?
Comment: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I lost my arms,\Nand lost my value as a weapon?
Comment: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just trained a little,\NI could still fight!
Comment: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. The war is over.
Comment: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the major's tool.
Comment: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he doesn't need me anymore,
Comment: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then I should be thrown away.
Comment: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw me away.
Comment: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw me away somewhere.
Comment: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Colonel Hodgins.
Comment: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot to tell you.
Comment: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I left the army.\NI'm not a Lt. Colonel anymore
Comment: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what should I call you?
Comment: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me "President."
Comment: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my company.
Comment: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought an old house\Nand renovated it a bit.
Comment: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The first floor is the reception.
Comment: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. Please write the receiver's\Nand sender's address on this form.
Comment: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow three days for delivery.
Comment: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The second floor houses the office\Nand the writing department.
Comment: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Writing?
Comment: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This department writes letters\Nat the requests of our clients.
Comment: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still many people\Nwho don't know how to write.
Comment: 0,0:12:57.07,0:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how to write either\Nuntil the major taught me how.
Comment: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about starting\Na business once the war ended.
Comment: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The government's postal service\Ndoesn't address the civilian's needs,
Comment: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so, I thought it would be\Na good opportunity.
Comment: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an order for you.
Comment: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet Evergarden.
Comment: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert left you with me.
Comment: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm giving you orders instead.
Comment: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still useful.
Comment: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can work. Here.
Comment: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Benedict.
Comment: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, President?
Comment: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to say\N"How can I help you, President?"
Comment: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's up?
Comment: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's up with you?\N-You did that on purpose!
Comment: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Benedict. He's a postman.
Comment: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an old friend\Nfrom before I started this company.
Comment: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Benedict, this is Violet.
Comment: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to work here\Nas a postman, starting today.
Comment: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a kid.
Comment: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's highly capable\Nof performing her duties.
Comment: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go to the bank.
Comment: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach her what she needs to know, got it?
Comment: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your stuff here.
Comment: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Comment: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uniform. Change.
Comment: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Comment: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! H... Hold on!
Comment: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's too big.
Comment: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a problem.
Comment: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better to take those off?
Comment: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it hard to sort the mail?
Comment: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not a big problem.
Comment: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort them just like it says here.\NPut them in those shelves.
Comment: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a huge pile of mail,\Nbut no need to rush.
Comment: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The break room is on the second floor.
Comment: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Comment: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Comment: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've almost completed my duties.
Comment: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you working the whole time?\NWithout taking a break?
Comment: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to long hours.
Comment: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, do you want to try\Ndelivering the mail?
Comment: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Delivering?
Comment: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You deliver the letter\Nto the address that's written on it.
Comment: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home now.
Comment: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"We will discuss financing\Nafter reviewing your performance." Right.
Comment: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like some companies\Ndo nighttime deliveries, too.
Comment: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't handle that.
Comment: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Comment: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Comment: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm delivering the mail.
Comment: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, mail delivery was meant for tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And make sure to take breaks during work.
Comment: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-You just got released from the hospital.\N-It's not a problem.
Comment: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It is a problem.
Comment: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet. Go ahead and eat.
Comment: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat.
Comment: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the office\Nonce you're done.
Comment: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have space in the attic,\Nbut you can sleep there.
Comment: 0,0:16:56.11,0:17:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, the Evergarden household\Nhas agreed to take you in...
Comment: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,until you become an adult.
Comment: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like leaving you\Nat the mansion...
Comment: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like there was a problem.
Comment: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Comment: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to put it nicely!
Comment: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How was I supposed to know?
Comment: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you home.
Comment: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the last order\Nyou received from Gilbert?
Comment: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "Run away and live freely."
Comment: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And, I...
Comment: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been in the army\Never since you were a child.
Comment: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've spent your life\Nfulfilling your duties.
Comment: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to learn a lot of things.
Comment: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it might be easier to keep living
Comment: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,if you didn't learn them,\Nif you didn't know them.
Comment: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't realize\Nthat your body is on fire
Comment: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and burning up\Nbecause of the things you did.
Comment: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not burning.
Comment: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are.
Comment: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not. You don't make sense.
Comment: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Comment: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You are burning.
Comment: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you like that, but left you alone.
Comment: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why when Gilbert\Nleft you with me,
Comment: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this was my chance.
Comment: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand one day.
Comment: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you'll realize for the first time\Nthat you have many burns.
Comment: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Doll?
Comment: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm Violet.
Comment: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Miss Violet.
Comment: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you\Nto write something for me.
Comment: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Write something?
Comment: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I don't know how to write.
Comment: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you write a letter for me?
Comment: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I write?
Comment: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to talk about it here?
Comment: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Comment: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Comment: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that my childhood friend\Nin the countryside
Comment: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,received a marriage offer\Nfrom another man. So...
Comment: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell her!
Comment: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"You were the first person
Comment: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,who was kind to me.
Comment: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You were everything to me.
Comment: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have done anything for you."
Comment: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Comment: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to know what you're feeling.
Comment: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to understand\Nwhat's in your heart.
Comment: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we're apart now...
Comment: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,love you."
Comment: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that?
Comment: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"I love you."
Comment: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to reception on the first floor\Nfor the delivery process.
Comment: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Comment: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for using\Nthe Auto Memory Doll Service.
Comment: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Who are you?
Comment: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Comment: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know\Nthat the man just now wanted to say
Comment: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"I love you"?
Comment: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to work as an Auto Memory Doll?
Comment: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's still hard for me to hold a pen.
Comment: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can operate a typewriter.
Comment: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I mean.
Comment: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask why\Nyou want to do this work.
Comment: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know!
Comment: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"I love you."
Comment: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what it means!
Comment: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The major said those words to me\Nafter he gave me my last orders.
Comment: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time\NI heard those words from the major.
Comment: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand...
Comment: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what that means.
Comment: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally,
Comment: 0,0:22:12.38,0:22:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,people become Auto Memory Dolls\Nbecause they understand that.
Comment: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Comment: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She had always just followed\NGilbert's orders in the past.
Comment: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time\Nshe asserted her own will.
Comment: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone said she didn't have a heart\Nand that she was a tool,
Comment: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but she said, "I want to know\Nwhat 'I love you' means."
Comment: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! There's no way\NI'm going to let you die!
Comment: 0,0:22:52.75,0:22:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Comment: 0,0:22:57.47,0:22:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop already!
Comment: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Live.
Comment: 0,0:23:10.31,0:23:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Comment: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Live, and...
Comment: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,be free.
Comment: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,From the bottom of my heart...
Comment: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Comment: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,À, ừ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Trung tá Hodgins?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bên này ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Không sao chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Có bị thương không?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thiếu tá đâu rồi ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thiếu tá Gilbert đâu rồi ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cậu ấy không có ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngài ấy đang ở đâu vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngài ấy về nhà nghỉ phép rồi ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Vết thương của ngài ấy ra sao rồi ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngài ấy bị thương rất nặng đấy ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thiếu tá... ngài ấy còn sống không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cậu ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Giờ em có thể xuất viện rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Trung tá Hodgins tới đây để đón em đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,À thì, đúng là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Xin phép ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Trung tá Hodgins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan, thư giãn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rất xin lỗi trung tá vì không nhớ được\N tên và quân hàm của ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Không sao, nào, ngồi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cơ mà, em vẫn nhớ tôi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng ta đã gặp nhau 2 lần, \Ntrong đợt huấn luyện và đêm trước trận quyết chiến ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Đúng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đang làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Viết báo cáo cho thiếu tá Gilbert ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Họ nói rằng cầm bút viết \Nrất có ích cho việc hồi phục ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy còn thiếu tá ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yên tâm đi, Violet-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cậu ấy nhờ tôi tới đây mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy tức là ngài ấy vẫn khoẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bác sĩ nói rằng quân ta đã thắng trận.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiện giờ thiếu tá đang làm nhiệm vụ gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Khi nào tôi mới được tham gia cùng ngài ấy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dù sao thì, em cứ thay đồ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Trong khi đợi, tôi sẽ cho người mang xe đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Đồ của em đấy, cuối cùng cũng chuyển tới.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hình như chúng bị chuyển nhầm \Ntới một quân khu xa lắc luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghim hoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiếc ghim hoa màu ngọc lục bảo đâu rồi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nơi họ tìm thấy em với ở quân khu có nhiêu đây thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nếu không có ở đây thì phải đi tìm mới được.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Đó là quà đấy ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Món quà thiếu tá Gilbert tặng đấy ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi biết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi sẽ tìm nó cho em.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi hứa đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dù sao thì, hãy đi cùng tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Đó là mệnh lệnh của cậu ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mệnh lệnh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rõ rồi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Đến khi nào thiếu tá mới ra lệnh tiếp cho tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,E rằng với tình trạng này sẽ có vài nhiệm vụ\N không thực hiện được.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúc mừng em xuất viện.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi không biết em thích cái nào, \Nnên đành mua hết cả 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Em thích con nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Không cần đâu ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Không được, em phải chọn,\N vờ như thế giới sắp tận diệt ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nào! Ba... hai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy con chó ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sao em lại chọn con chó?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Anh trai của thiếu tá từng nói rằng \N"Mày là con chó của Gilbert".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chuyến đi sẽ khá dài đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do bị địch đánh bom nên đường sắt\N quanh đây đều bị hư hỏng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Em tới Leiden lần nào chưa nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Chưa ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Em ở đây à.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:07:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Trung tá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thấy cảng Leiden rồi kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert rất lo cho tính mạng của em sau chiến tranh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nên cậu ấy đã nhờ tôi gửi gắm em \Ncho nhà Evergarden,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,họ hàng thân tín của cậu ấy chăm sóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Khi gọi điện hỏi thì hai ông bà \Nđều sẵn lòng chào đón em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hai người tới rồi ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nào, Violet-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Đây là bà Evergarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chào bà ấy đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,À, cúi chào là được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Đi từ Enchaine về đây mất tận 3 ngày à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Vâng, thường thì về đây chỉ mất có 1 ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiến tranh kéo dài tận 4 năm mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Phải mất một thời gian nữa \Nmọi thứ mới phục hồi được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nào, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uống trà đi cháu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta xin lỗi, không cần cố quá đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nguy rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cháu sẽ bị bỏng mất!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Không sao đâu ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Cháu không thấy nóng đâu ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhưng cũng phải mau làm mát lớp băng bó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oliver, mang ít đá lạnh tới đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Vâng ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tay cháu được làm từ adamantine ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuy nhìn hơi thô kệch, nhưng rất bền ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuy vẫn chưa quen, nhưng cháu \Nsẽ học cách điều chỉnh nó dần.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cháu qua đây chút được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hồi trẻ ta từng đeo đôi găng tay này.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhìn được đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đeo thử đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhìn hợp đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Đúng thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy, cháu đi nhé...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cháu còn phải về công ty nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,nhớ ngoan ngoãn vâng lời Tiffany-san nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Không sao đâu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Không cần lo cho bà đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Cứ coi ta như mẹ ruột của cháu là được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nếu có gì thì cứ nói ra, nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cháu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,không có cha mẹ, nên là,\N cháu không cần thứ gì thay thế đâu ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Đừng nói vậy chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta từng có một đứa con trai,\N nhưng nó đã mất trong chiến tranh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Cháu không thể thay thế\N người con trai quá cố của bà được ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert muốn em sống hạnh phúc ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Em hiểu chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thiếu tá...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tại sao thiếu tá Gilbert lại bỏ tôi ở lại đây ạ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Có phải vì tôi đã mất tay và cả vai trò vũ khí không ạ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nếu luyện tập thì tôi vẫn có thể chiến đấu được!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan, chiến tranh đã chấm dứt rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi là công cụ của thiếu tá.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nếu ngài ấy không cần tôi nữa,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,thì tôi nên bị vứt đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Xin ngài hãy vứt tôi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hãy vứt tôi ở đâu đó đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Trung tá Hodgins...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Quên chưa nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi rời quân ngũ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Giờ tôi không còn là trung tá nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy tôi nên gọi ngài thế nào đây ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Giám đốc"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Đây là công ty của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi đã mua 1 căn biệt thự cũ rồi sửa sang lại chút ít.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tầng trệt là lễ tân.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Quý khách, phiền ngài viết địa chỉ\N người gửi và người nhận vào đây ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Việc chuyển hàng cần khoảng 3 ngày ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Văn phòng và bộ phận nhận viết thư thì ở tầng 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Viết thư?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Đó là bộ phận nhận viết thư \Ntheo yêu cầu của khách hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Vẫn còn nhiều người không biết viết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi cũng không viết được...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...trước khi được thiếu tá dạy cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thế à...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi từng tính sẽ lập nghiệp \Nsau khi chiến tranh kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dịch vụ bưu chính của chính phủ \Nthì vẫn chưa cho dân thường dùng,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,nên tôi tính tận dụng cơ hội này.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Đây là mệnh lệnh, Violet Evergarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert giao em lại cho tôi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,nên tôi sẽ ra lệnh thay cậu ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Em vẫn còn hữu dụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hãy làm việc...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,ở đây nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Benedict.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Chuyện gì thế giám đốc?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ý cậu là "Tôi có thể làm gì cho giám đốc" phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy? Chuyện gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Này, cái gì vậy hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cậu cố ý nói vậy chứ gì!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cậu ấy là Benedict, nhân viên đưa thư.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cậu ta là bạn cũ của tôi\N từ trước khi thành lập công ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,, Benedict, đây là Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Từ nay cô ấy sẽ là nhân viên ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Con nhóc này à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cô bé giỏi thực hiện nhiệm vụ lắm đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi tới ngân hàng đây,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,nhờ cậu chỉ bảo cô ấy nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Đồ đạc để trong này nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Đã rõ ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Đồng phục.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thay đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Đã rõ ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Cô làm g—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Này, khoan đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hơi rộng nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Không sao đâu ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cởi cái đó ra không được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sắp xếp bưu phẩm khó khăn lắm à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Không, không vấn đề gì to tát đâu ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Xếp chúng theo tên được viết ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rồi sắp vào kệ đặt ở kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bưu kiện còn nhiều lắm, nhưng không cần cố quá đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Phòng nghỉ trên tầng 2 nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Đã rõ ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi sắp hoàn thành nhiệm vụ rồi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Làm nãy giờ đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Không nghỉ tay luôn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi đã quen với việc thực hiện \Nchiến dịch trong nhiều giờ rồi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy, tiếp theo có muốn thử đi đưa thư không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Đưa thư?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chuyển thư với địa chỉ ghi trên bì thư ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy, tôi về đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hẹn mai gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chúng tôi sẽ xem xét đầu tư dựa trên\N thành quả mà ngài đạt được" à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Vài công ty còn giao hàng ban đêm nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Công ty của mình vẫn chưa làm được nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Em làm cái gì thế hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Đưa thư ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi nói đưa thư ý là ngày mai cơ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mà, em cũng phải nghỉ ngơi trong khi làm việc đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chỉ vừa mới xuất viện thôi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Không sao đâu ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cô thật là, có sao đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Em ăn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Xin phép ngài ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ăn xong cùng tôi về công ty nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuy chỉ còn gác mái trống, \Nnhưng tôi đã dọn dẹp để em ngủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,À, nhà Evergarden nói là rất sẵn lòng cho em ở lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,cho đến khi em trưởng thành.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhưng để em sống ở ngôi biệt thự thì có hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hơi có vấn đề đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thằng nhóc này, có thấy tôi\N đang cố trấn an con bé không hả!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:10.91,Default,,0,0,40,,{\an8}Đau đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai thèm quan tâm chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy, mai gặp lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi đi bộ cùng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lệnh cuối cùng em nhận từ Gilbert là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chạy đi, và sống thật tự do."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Và còn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Từ khi còn nhỏ, em đã ở trong quân đội,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,chỉ biết mỗi việc hoàn thành nhiệm vụ được giao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhưng từ giờ em sẽ học được nhiều thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhưng nếu không học hỏi, nếu không biết gì \Nthì biết đâu em sẽ sống hạnh phúc hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Em vẫn chưa nhận ra rằng\N những việc mình làm cho đến giờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,đã dấy thành ngọn lửa thiêu đốt con người em.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Không có lửa đốt ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Có đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Không có mà, ngài nói lạ thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Em đang bị thiêu đốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Khi nhìn em như thế, tôi đã lờ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nên khi được Gilbert giao cho, \Ntôi đã nghĩ đây là cơ hội để bù đắp cho em.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Một ngày nào đó, em sẽ hiểu những lời tôi nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Và đó cũng là lần đầu tiên em thấy\N cơ thể mình có rất nhiều vết bỏng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cô... Hình Nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Không, tôi là Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,À, cô Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi muốn nhờ cô viết một bức thư.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Viết thư?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi không biết viết.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nên là tôi muốn nhờ cô thay tôi viết 1 bức thư.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi nên viết gì đây ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Có nhất thiết phải nói ra ở đây không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Có vấn đề gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi nghe nói bạn thuở nhỏ của mình ở nông thôn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,được một tên đàn ông khác cầu hôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi muốn nói cho cô ấy biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...vẫn mãi yêu em.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Như thế đã được chưa ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“Anh vẫn mãi yêu em.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Giờ thì, phiền ngài mang nó đến \Nlễ tân ở tầng trệt để làm thủ tục gửi thư ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn quý khách đã sử dụng \Ndịch vụ Hình Nhân Ghi Chép Tự Động.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Cô đây là?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sao cô lại biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sao cô lại biết lúc nãy ông ấy \Nmuốn nói “Anh vẫn mãi yêu em”?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Em muốn làm Hình Nhân Ghi Chép Tự Động ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuy cầm bút còn khó khăn, \Nnhưng tôi vẫn có thể dùng máy đánh chữ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,À không, tôi chỉ muốn hỏi tại sao \Nlại là công việc đó thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi muốn biết...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,“Tôi yêu em”, tôi muốn hiểu câu nói đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sau khi nhận mệnh lệnh cuối cùng của thiếu tá,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ngài ấy đã nói câu đó với tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Đó là lần đầu tiên tôi nghe thiếu tá nói câu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lời đó có ý nghĩa gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tôi không tài nào hiểu được ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thường thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.34,0:22:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiểu được câu đó mới có thể \Nlàm Hình Nhân Ghi Chép Tự Động.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.91,0:22:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Được thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:21.92,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:25.05,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Có mắt của thiếu tá ở đây ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:29.71,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Nó có màu giống với mắt thiếu tá ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:36.66,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Khi nhìn nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:39.64,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,...cảm xúc này...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:44.91,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,...là gì...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.66,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Violet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.31,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Hãy sống...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.75,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,...thật tự do...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.01,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Từ tận đáy lòng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.13,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Đi mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:48.46,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Nhất định, nhất định em sẽ không để\N thiếu tá chết đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:54.04,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Dừng lại...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:58.92,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Dừng lại đi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.55,0:23:05.51,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Hãy sống...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:11.60,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Violet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:15.29,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Em phải sống...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.11,0:23:17.94,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,...thật tự do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:25.20,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Từ đáy lòng mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:32.89,Default - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Tôi yêu em!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.40,0:01:21.30,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Thiếu tá Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:23.60,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Hôm nay là ngày nằm viện thứ 120.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:26.71,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Thể lực đã hồi phục gần như hoàn toàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:31.55,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Tuy cử động còn khó khăn, \Nnhưng em vẫn có thể làm nhiệm vụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:34.55,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Yêu cầu trở lại làm nhiệm vụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:40.61,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Sự tồn tại của cô bé được giấu kín đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:45.71,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Nhưng những người biết cô bé \Nnói rằng cô chỉ là một món vũ khí...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:50.92,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,chiến đấu theo lệnh được giao \Ntrong dáng dấp con người.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.97,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Một công cụ không có lấy trái tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:55.40,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,“Người đầu tiên đối xử tốt với anh, chính là em.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:00.65,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Với anh, em như cả thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:07.11,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Vì em, anh sẵn lòng làm mọi thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.42,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Anh muốn thấu hiểu cảm xúc của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.14,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Anh muốn thấu hiểu con tim em.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.96,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Giờ đây, dù hai ta có xa cách...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.60,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Thì anh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:29.24,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Người con gái chỉ tuân lệnh của mỗi Gilbert,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:32.37,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,đó là lần đầu tiên cô bé nói lên lý tưởng của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:36.27,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,Người con gái bị gọi là\N công cụ không có lấy trái tim...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:39.03,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,nói rằng muốn biết ý nghĩa của câu “Tôi yêu em”.
